metadata.name: Louis Vuitton Skull and Crossbones 1
metadata.description: Life sized gold leafed skull and crossbones on Louis Vuitton canvas covered hardboard with gold hardware and gold leafed frame with an actual Louis Vuitton Confidential Bandeau scarf. 20x 20x 9 inches. This is a one of a kind art piece #1 on the Fashion to Die For collection.
